Eddystone
---------

![](pics/eddystone.png){.align-center width="200px"}

<https://developers.google.com/beacons/>

Eddystone is a protocol specification that defines a Bluetooth low
energy (BLE) message format for proximity beacon messages. It describes
several different frame types that may be used individually or in
combinations to create beacons that can be used for a variety of
applications.
